OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fsome patchy light rain through the
OL,7,Fevening. Then staying cloudy overnight
OL,8,Fwith some heavier bursts of rain
OL,9,Fdeveloping towards morning. A mild
OL,10,Fnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FLargely cloudy as bands of
OL,13,Frain push northeast in the morning.
OL,14,FTurning showery later, these showers
OL,15,Fheavy and thundery at times.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FBright spells and showers from the
OL,19,Fwest on Thursday. A further rain band
OL,20,Fpushes northeast on Friday. Bright
OL,21,Fspells and showers again on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
